# Sales Tracker (Python CLI App)

This is a beginner Python project that allows users to:
- Add sales
- View sales
- Calculate total profit
- Exit program

## Features
- Uses lists and dictionaries to store data
- Uses loops and conditionals for interaction
- Calculates profit dynamically

## What I learned
- Python basics (input, loops, if statements)
- Data structures (lists and dictionaries)
- Program flow and user interaction